{"id": "art-1539", "label": "Art. 1539", "title": "Art. 1539", "slug": "art-1539", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1319593755\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2101\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1319593755\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>9</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_550592201\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2100\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_550592201\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Consiliul de\nsupraveghere are urm&#259;toarele <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span>\nprincipale:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_618400306\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2099\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_618400306\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)exercit&#259; controlul permanent asupra conducerii <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> de c&#259;tre directorat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1643759670\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2098\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1643759670\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>nume&#351;te</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> revoc&#259; membrii directoratului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_18624420\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2097\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_18624420\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)verific&#259; conformitatea cu <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legea</i>, cu actul constitutiv <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu\nhot&#259;rârile adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span>\nde conducere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1129061745\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2096\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1129061745\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)raporteaz&#259; cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\no dat&#259; pe an adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\ncu privire la activitatea de supraveghere <span class=SpellE>desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_938162776\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2095\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_938162776\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazuri <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ionale</span>,\ncând interesul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> o cere, consiliul\nde supraveghere poate convoca adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1251632549\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2094\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1251632549\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Consiliului de supraveghere nu îi pot fi transferate <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span> de conducere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nCu toate acestea, în actul constitutiv se poate prevedea c&#259; anumite tipuri\nde <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> nu pot fi efectuate decât cu\nacordul consiliului. În cazul în care consiliul nu <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nd&#259; acordul pentru o astfel de <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>,\ndirectoratul poate cere acordul adun&#259;rii generale ordinare. Hot&#259;rârea\nadun&#259;rii generale cu privire la un asemenea acord este dat&#259; cu o\nmajoritate de 3 p&#259;trimi din num&#259;rul voturilor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>. Actul constitutiv nu poate stabili o\nalt&#259; majoritate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nici stipula alte <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}